Опубликованные закупки на 2016 год
Количество опубликованных ОЗ с финансированием на 2016 год в Планах закупок на 2018-2019 годы

Количество объектов закупок, для которых выполняются условия:

  1. ОЗ опубликован;
  2. Дата публикации Плана закупок, к которому относится ОЗ не пустая и лежит внутри отчетного периода;
  3. План закупок создан на год, установленный в параметре управления отчетом "Год плана закупок";
  4. ОЗ имеет финансирование на установленный в параметре управления отчетом "Год финансирования".

Объем закупаемой на 2016 год продукции по опубликованным ДОЗ с финансированием на 2016 год в Планах-графиках на 2016 год

Объем закупок в натуральном выражении в году, установленном в параметре управления "Год финансирования" в соответствии с планом поставок ДОЗ, для которых выполняются условия:

  1. ДОЗ опубликован;

  3. План график сформирован на выбранный в параметрах управления отчетом год плана-графика;
  4. ДОЗ имеет финансирование на установленный в параметре управления отчетом "Год финансирования";
  5. Дата закупки относится к году финансирования.

             R,

          LEFT JOIN (
            SELECT MENU_ID m_id, MIN(R) AS R, MIN(
              CASE WHEN R > 0 THEN W ELSE 0 END
            ) AS W
            FROM CORE_ADMIN_MSK. V_USER_PRIVS VUP

          ) S ON RCM.MENU_ID||'' = S.M_ID||''
           WHERE R > 0 AND ENABLED=1 
          ORDER BY N_ORDER, NAME

17data_inp 0.001:
SELECT
	t.*,
	COUNT(1) OVER() AS visible_rows
FROM
(
	SELECT
		ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY id DESC) AS rn,
		id,
		current_state,
		filesize,
		report_content,
   		TO_CHAR(d_req, 'DD.MM.YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AS d_req,
   		TO_CHAR(d_last, 'DD.MM.YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AS d_last,
   		id_report,
   		canceled,
   		s_name
	FROM
		t_report_req
	WHERE
		is_enabled = 1 AND
		is_mail = 0 AND
		id_user = :id_user/* AND
		downloaded = 0*/
) t
WHERE
	(:id_req > 0 AND :id_req = t.id) OR
	t.rn BETWEEN :start_num_row AND :last_num_row
bound id_user as INT 21=1 bound start_num_row as INT 21=1 bound last_num_row as INT 21=10 bound id_req as INT 21=0

SELECT
                    id AS id,
                    CASE
                    WHEN regexp_like(sys_context('eaist_context','org'), id||',') THEN null
                    ElSE id_parent
                    END AS parent_id,
                    formatted_name AS name,
                     CASE WHEN (id = '0_2' or id_level=min_level) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS opened, 
                     CASE WHEN (row_count=1 or id_level=min_level or id_level=min_level+1) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS default_selected, 
                    KEY_SORT s_key_sort
                    FROM
                    (select dat.id, dat.id_parent, dat.formatted_name, dat.id_level, f.row_count, dat.KEY_SORT, min(dat.id_level) over() min_level from
                    (
                    select id||'_'||id_source as id, id_parent||'_'||id_parent_source as id_parent, id_level, formatted_name, is_aggregator, rn as KEY_SORT from (
                    SELECT 0 id,2 id_source,NULL id_parent,NULL id_parent_source,1 id_level,'Итого по городу' formatted_name,0 is_aggregator,0 rn FROM DUAL
                    UNION all
                    SELECT
                    	id,id_source,id_parent,id_parent_source,id_level,formatted_name,is_aggregator,rn
                    from sp_customers_tree
                    where version_date=to_date(:version_date,'dd.mm.yyyy') AND is_archive=0                    
                    )) dat
                    
                    join (select f.*, count(*) over() row_count from(
                    select id from lnk_customers_all_level where version_date =to_date(:version_date, 'dd.mm.yyyy') and id_parent in  (select replace(regexp_substr(orgs, '([[:digit:]]*_[[:digit:]]*,)', 1, rownum), ',') org_id
                                                                                                                                      from (select sys_context('eaist_context','org') orgs From dual)
                                                                                                                                      connect by  regexp_count(orgs, '\,')+1>rownum)
                    union
                    select replace(regexp_substr(orgs, '([[:digit:]]*_[[:digit:]]*,)', 1, rownum), ',') org_id
                    from (select sys_context('eaist_context','org') orgs From dual)
                    connect by  regexp_count(orgs, '\,')+1>rownum)f) f on f.id=dat.id
                    WHERE formatted_name NOT IN ('Архив', 'Прочие')
                    
                    )

SELECT
    id,
    parent_id,
    indicator_id,
    name,
    level,
    description,
    DISPLAY_BY_DEFAULT,
    IS_PERIOD,
    IS_BUDGET_YEAR,
    IS_PLAN_PERIOD,
    IS_PLAN_YEAR,
    IS_PERIOD_SEND_REQUEST,
    IS_PERIOD_SEND_CONCLUS,
    ORD
FROM
(
    SELECT
        bh.block_id AS id,
        b.parent_id,
        b.indicator_id,
        b.name,
        i.description_br AS description,
        bh.DISPLAY_BY_DEFAULT,
        b.IS_PERIOD,
        b.IS_BUDGET_YEAR,
        b.IS_PLAN_PERIOD,
        b.IS_PLAN_YEAR,
        b.IS_PERIOD_SEND_REQUEST,
        b.IS_PERIOD_SEND_CONCLUS,
        bh.ORD
    FROM
        s_lnk_block_header bh
    INNER JOIN
        s_sp_block b
        ON
            b.id = bh.block_id
    LEFT JOIN
        f_sp_indicators i
        ON
            i.entity_id = b.indicator_id and :VERSION_DATE between DATE_START and DATE_END 
    WHERE
        bh.header_id IN
        (
            SELECT
                h.id
            FROM
                s_sp_reports r
            INNER JOIN
                s_sp_header h
                ON
                    h.report_id = r.id
            WHERE
                r.id = :REPORT_ID
        )
    ORDER BY
        bh.ORD
)
CONNECT BY
    PRIOR id = parent_id
START WITH
    parent_id IS NULL
    ORDER SIBLINGS BY ORD
bound REPORT_ID as INT 21=12 bound VERSION_DATE as SQLT_CHR good 03.04.2018 (10)

string(1454) "
with cols as (
    SELECT slnk.block_id AS id,slnk.header_id,slnk.display_by_default,b.parent_id,b.name,b.indicator_id,slnk.ord,slnk.block_id,NVL(dt.name, case when ind.unit_id between 1 and 4 then 'digital' else 'text' end) unit,
        ind.CUBE_1LVL_ID,ind.calculate_formula,lbdh.d_header_id
    from s_lnk_block_header slnk
    LEFT JOIN s_sp_block b ON b.id = slnk.block_id
    left join S_LNK_BLOCK_D_HEADER lbdh on lbdh.block_id = b.id and lbdh.det = 0
    left join f_sp_indicators ind on ind.entity_id = b.indicator_id and TO_DATE (SYS_CONTEXT ('eaist_context', 'version_date'),'DD.MM.YYYY') between DATE_START and DATE_END
    left join s_sp_datatype_web dt on dt.id = ind.datatype_web_id
    WHERE slnk.header_id IN
        (   SELECT h.id
            FROM s_sp_reports sp
            LEFT JOIN s_sp_header h ON h.report_id = sp.id
            WHERE sp.id = 12)
    ORDER BY slnk.ord
),
cols2 as (
  SELECT s.id,s.name,s.indicator_id,COUNT(s.id) AS colspan,s.parent_id,level,MAX(level) OVER() AS max_level,s.ord,s.unit,s.CUBE_1LVL_ID,s.calculate_formula,s.block_id,s.d_header_id
    FROM cols s
    GROUP BY s.id,s.name,s.indicator_id,s.parent_id,level,s.ord,s.unit,s.CUBE_1LVL_ID,s.calculate_formula,s.block_id,s.d_header_id
    CONNECT BY PRIOR s.parent_id = s.id
    START WITH  s.id IN (335, 336, 339, 341, 342, 345, 347, 348, 351) 
)
SELECT s.*
FROM cols2 s
CONNECT BY s.parent_id = s.id
ORDER SIBLINGS By s.ord"

select a.*, 1-connect_by_isleaf CHILDCOUNT, sys_connect_by_path( id , ',' ) PARENTS , level lvl from(

/*id_organization_merge*/
SELECT
                    id AS id,
                    CASE
                    WHEN regexp_like(sys_context('eaist_context','org'), id||',') THEN null
                    ElSE id_parent
                    END AS parent_id,
                    formatted_name AS name,
                     CASE WHEN (id = '0_2' or id_level=min_level) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS opened, 
                     CASE WHEN (row_count=1 or id_level=min_level or id_level=min_level+1) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS default_selected, 
                    KEY_SORT s_key_sort
                    FROM
                    (select dat.id, dat.id_parent, dat.formatted_name, dat.id_level, f.row_count, dat.KEY_SORT, min(dat.id_level) over() min_level from
                    (
                    select id||'_'||id_source as id, id_parent||'_'||id_parent_source as id_parent, id_level, formatted_name, is_aggregator, rn as KEY_SORT from (
                    SELECT 0 id,2 id_source,NULL id_parent,NULL id_parent_source,1 id_level,'Итого по городу' formatted_name,0 is_aggregator,0 rn FROM DUAL
                    UNION all
                    SELECT
                    	id,id_source,id_parent,id_parent_source,id_level,formatted_name,is_aggregator,rn
                    from sp_customers_tree
                    where version_date=to_date(:version_date,'dd.mm.yyyy') AND is_archive=0                    
                    )) dat
                    
                    join (select f.*, count(*) over() row_count from(
                    select id from lnk_customers_all_level where version_date =to_date(:version_date, 'dd.mm.yyyy') and id_parent in  (select replace(regexp_substr(orgs, '([[:digit:]]*_[[:digit:]]*,)', 1, rownum), ',') org_id
                                                                                                                                      from (select sys_context('eaist_context','org') orgs From dual)
                                                                                                                                      connect by  regexp_count(orgs, '\,')+1>rownum)
                    union
                    select replace(regexp_substr(orgs, '([[:digit:]]*_[[:digit:]]*,)', 1, rownum), ',') org_id
                    from (select sys_context('eaist_context','org') orgs From dual)
                    connect by  regexp_count(orgs, '\,')+1>rownum)f) f on f.id=dat.id
                    WHERE formatted_name NOT IN ('Архив', 'Прочие')
                    
                    )
/**/

) a

connect by nocycle prior id= parent_id
start with (parent_id = :START_WITH and :START_WITH is not null) or (:START_WITH is null and parent_id is null) 
 order BY s_key_sort

SELECT
    id,
    parent_id,
    indicator_id,
    name,
    level,
    description,
    DISPLAY_BY_DEFAULT,
    IS_PERIOD,
    IS_BUDGET_YEAR,
    IS_PLAN_PERIOD,
    IS_PLAN_YEAR,
    IS_PERIOD_SEND_REQUEST,
    IS_PERIOD_SEND_CONCLUS,
    ORD
FROM
(
    SELECT
        bh.block_id AS id,
        b.parent_id,
        b.indicator_id,
        b.name,
        i.description_br AS description,
        bh.DISPLAY_BY_DEFAULT,
        b.IS_PERIOD,
        b.IS_BUDGET_YEAR,
        b.IS_PLAN_PERIOD,
        b.IS_PLAN_YEAR,
        b.IS_PERIOD_SEND_REQUEST,
        b.IS_PERIOD_SEND_CONCLUS,
        bh.ORD
    FROM
        s_lnk_block_header bh
    INNER JOIN
        s_sp_block b
        ON
            b.id = bh.block_id
    LEFT JOIN
        f_sp_indicators i
        ON
            i.entity_id = b.indicator_id and TO_DATE (SYS_CONTEXT ('eaist_context', 'version_date'),'DD.MM.YYYY') between DATE_START and DATE_END 
    WHERE
        bh.header_id IN
        (
            SELECT
                h.id
            FROM
                s_sp_reports r
            INNER JOIN
                s_sp_header h
                ON
                    h.report_id = r.id
            WHERE
                r.id = :REPORT_ID
        )
    ORDER BY
        bh.ORD
)
CONNECT BY
    PRIOR id = parent_id
START WITH
    parent_id IS NULL
    ORDER SIBLINGS BY ORD
bound REPORT_ID as INT 21=12

with cols as (
    SELECT slnk.block_id AS id,slnk.header_id,slnk.display_by_default,b.parent_id,b.name,b.indicator_id,slnk.ord,slnk.block_id,NVL(dt.name, case when ind.unit_id between 1 and 4 then 'digital' else 'text' end) unit,
        ind.CUBE_1LVL_ID,ind.calculate_formula,lbdh.d_header_id
    from s_lnk_block_header slnk
    LEFT JOIN s_sp_block b ON b.id = slnk.block_id
    left join S_LNK_BLOCK_D_HEADER lbdh on lbdh.block_id = b.id and lbdh.det = 0
    left join f_sp_indicators ind on ind.entity_id = b.indicator_id and TO_DATE (SYS_CONTEXT ('eaist_context', 'version_date'),'DD.MM.YYYY') between DATE_START and DATE_END
    left join s_sp_datatype_web dt on dt.id = ind.datatype_web_id
    WHERE slnk.header_id IN
        (   SELECT h.id
            FROM s_sp_reports sp
            LEFT JOIN s_sp_header h ON h.report_id = sp.id
            WHERE sp.id = 12)
    ORDER BY slnk.ord
),
cols2 as (
  SELECT s.id,s.name,s.indicator_id,COUNT(s.id) AS colspan,s.parent_id,level,MAX(level) OVER() AS max_level,s.ord,s.unit,s.CUBE_1LVL_ID,s.calculate_formula,s.block_id,s.d_header_id
    FROM cols s
    GROUP BY s.id,s.name,s.indicator_id,s.parent_id,level,s.ord,s.unit,s.CUBE_1LVL_ID,s.calculate_formula,s.block_id,s.d_header_id
    CONNECT BY PRIOR s.parent_id = s.id
    START WITH  s.id IN (335, 336, 339, 341, 342, 345, 347, 348, 351) 
)
SELECT s.*
FROM cols2 s
CONNECT BY s.parent_id = s.id
ORDER SIBLINGS By s.ord

            ENABLED, SUBTITLE, MODULE,
             R,
             W
          FROM MSK_EAIST_ANALYTIC.rep_core_menu RCM
          LEFT JOIN (
            SELECT MENU_ID m_id, MIN(R) AS R, MIN(
              CASE WHEN R > 0 THEN W ELSE 0 END
            ) AS W
            FROM CORE_ADMIN_MSK. V_USER_PRIVS VUP
            LEFT JOIN CORE_ADMIN_MSK. T_MENU_PRIVS TMP ON TMP.PRIV_ID = VUP.PRIV_ID

              VUP.SYS_ID=777 AND NOT MENU_ID IS NULL
            GROUP BY MENU_ID
          ) S ON RCM.MENU_ID||'' = S.M_ID||''
           WHERE R > 0 AND ENABLED=1 
          ORDER BY N_ORDER, NAME

17data_inp 0.001:
SELECT
	t.*,
	COUNT(1) OVER() AS visible_rows
FROM
(
	SELECT
		ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY id DESC) AS rn,
		id,
		current_state,
		filesize,
		report_content,
   		TO_CHAR(d_req, 'DD.MM.YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AS d_req,
   		TO_CHAR(d_last, 'DD.MM.YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AS d_last,
   		id_report,
   		canceled,
   		s_name
	FROM
		t_report_req
	WHERE
		is_enabled = 1 AND
		is_mail = 0 AND
		id_user = :id_user/* AND
		downloaded = 0*/
) t
WHERE
	(:id_req > 0 AND :id_req = t.id) OR
	t.rn BETWEEN :start_num_row AND :last_num_row
bound id_user as INT 21=1 bound start_num_row as INT 21=1 bound last_num_row as INT 21=10 bound id_req as INT 21=0
